  "instructions": [
    "In a large bowl, whisk together yogurt, olive oil, smoked paprika, garlic, salt, and pepper.",
    "Add lamb cubes to the marinade and mix until coated. Cover and refrigerate for at least 2 hours or overnight.",
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat. Thread marinated lamb onto skewers.",
    "Grill kebabs for 8-10 minutes per side, or until lamb reaches an internal temperature of 145°F (63°C).",
    "Transfer kebabs to a serving platter. Garnish with fresh oregano and serve with lemon wedges.",
    "Let kebabs rest for 5 minutes before serving. Serve hot."
